column4: Hmmm.. I can get it from a remote location with wget.. I wonder what's up?
udo u really want to know?
u think MSCE are stupid? have u try troubleshooting BSODs and stuff? Or recovering from a corrupted IIS metabase?

well then u have a point LOL
